message.entry: Automated single-precision conversion using MATLAB Coder projects is no longer supported. The specified project will be imported into the MATLAB Coder app with single-precision conversion disabled. To use single-precision conversion, convert the project to a MATLAB script and continue using the command-line workflow. For more information, see Converting Code Generation Projects to MATLAB Scripts.

Automated fixed-point conversion using MATLAB Coder projects is no longer supported. The specified project will be imported into the MATLAB Coder app with fixed-point conversion disabled. To use fixed-point conversion, convert the project to a MATLAB script and continue using the command-line workflow. For more information, see Converting Code Generation Projects to MATLAB Scripts.

The Fixed-Point Converter app is no longer available. Convert the project to a MATLAB script and continue using the command-line workflow. For more information, see Convert Fixed-Point Conversion Project to MATLAB Scripts.
